  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add pork belly slices and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove pork from skillet and set aside.",
    "Add diced onion and bell pepper to skillet and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add sliced almonds to skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add cumin, chili powder, salt, and pepper to skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Return pork to skillet and stir to combine with vegetable mixture.",
    "Warm tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble fajitas by placing pork and vegetable mixture onto tortillas and serving immediately."
